name: Violinist
description:
Biancha Bianchi, daughter of Italians, was a known violinist in Curitiba/BR, she died at 98 years old, her music school is now a residential condominium in the center of Curitiba, where I live.
In this tomb are present his father, mother and sister who died as a child.

made with photogrammetry / 2022 - Higor Casagrande
